mor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-768x426.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-1536x852.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-696x385.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-1920x1066.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/26164923/Bosch-eBike_Graphic_Riding_Mode_Tour__EN1-757x420.jpg 757w\"></p><p>Bosch Tour+ is available as a software upgrade for any eBike equipped with the Bosch Performance Line CX motor and derailleur system. For more information, check out <a href=\"https://www.bosch-ebike.com/us/service/dealer-search#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bosch’s find-a-dealer page</a>.</p></div></div>","author":"Sam Anderson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"cb264a7966c6bb8c0945e512b3258b2087789ab1d17e5c13ec4338ef5697b9c1","category":"Cycling"}